<s> I have to disagree on this:  </s>
<s> There is no such thing as universal sign language.  </s>
<s> Each community's sign language is a naturally formed language with it's own phonology, morphology, and syntax.  </s>
<s> If a Deaf American and a Deaf German meet on the street, they *won't* understand each other.  </s>
<s> What they *will* be better at is a mutual gesturing.  </s>
<s> Since they both use language through a visual medium, they're more receptive to communicating physically.  </s>
